# surge

> Simple command-line web publishing
> More information: https://surge.sh

- Upload a new site to surge.sh:

`surge {string value: path/to/my_project}`

- Deploy site to custom domain (note that the DNS records must point to the surge.sh subdomain):

`surge {string value: path/to/my_project} {string value: my_custom_domain.com}`

- List your surge projects:

`surge list`

- Remove a project:

`surge teardown {string value: my_custom_domain.com}`
